title: blackScreen
---
//out with friends
<<if has_flag("intent_to_leave")>>
  <<play_sound "barAmbience">>
  Yay! Jenny's here!
  How are things since...?
  Have you heard that...
  You should come out more often!
  See you next time!
  <<unset_flag "intent_to_leave">>
  <<set_flag "broken_house">>
  <<stop_sound "barAmbience">>
  <<load_scene_fade "frontHouse">>
<<elseif has_flag("game_over")>>
  The End.
<<else>>
 How did you get here?
 You're not supposed to be here yet.
<<endif>>
===
